title: equation and basic
link: https://www.investopedia.com/trading/getting-to-know-the-greeks/
      https://www.investopedia.com/terms/k/kappa.asp
tag: fianance, basic
status: none
summary:
Vega: Measures Impact of a Change in Volatility
Theta: Measures Impact of a Change in Time Remaining
Delta: Measures Impact of a Change in the Price of Underlying
Gamma: Measures the Rate of Change of Delta
Kappa: measurement of an option contract's price sensitivity to changes in the volatility of the underlying asset, also called vega
